description: A taste of the Emerald Isle in Oklahoma City--this great truck is ready to bring Irish Fusion to the food truck world! Irish-infused flavors are what sets St. Paddy Cakes apart. Whether it's the Irish Potato Cakes, the kettle chip nachos with Guinness-infused white cheddar, or anything off their amazing menu, you'll be blown away by the delicious flavors and fantastic service at St. Paddy Cakes!
name: St. Paddy Cakes
